    • banknotesLoaded

      default void banknotesLoaded(IBanknoteDispenser dispenser, Banknote... banknotes)
      Called to announce that the indicated sequence of banknotes has been added to the indicated banknote dispenser. Used to simulate direct, physical loading of the dispenser.
      Parameters:
      dispenser - The dispenser where the event occurred.
      banknotes - The banknotes that were loaded.

      default void banknotesUnloaded(IBanknoteDispenser dispenser, Banknote... banknotes)

      banknotes - The banknotes that were unloaded.
